My granddaughter was the one that told us about the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Mickey's Sport-Y-Thon and that she would like it for the medal. Her father has many medals and she wanted some too.  Her mother explained that her father worked hard for his medals.  Anyway, she loves the medal.

Grandkids love it!
Great....Mouskeball is one of her favorite episodes.  Sport-Y-Thon is a great Olympic style sports story.  She really enjoys this dvd.

Since Amazon doesn't let you see the back of these DVDs.....

The episodes included are

Mickeys Sport-Y-Thon (hasn't shown on TV)
Mickeys Mousekeball! (episode 5-2)
Donalds Brand New Clubhouse (episode 5-3)
Mickeys Mousekedoer Adventure (episode 5-4)
Mickeys Mystery! (episode 4-8)
Mickeys Happy Mousekeday (episode 4-14)

We will probably be buying this one too!
